item.title: Need help please - Re: changing teleport locations and official server name -
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“playregzz, post:9, topic:550576”]dude you’ve gone way off what i requested.
Read my OT…

Im asking NOTHING to do with the interface, description, or title of the teleports.
Im merely asking how to change Home teleports delivery co-ordinates, nothing youve said is relevant to this.

Go away now, your just trying to get post count[/quote]
I apologize for miss-reading what you were trying to do.

Have you looked in ClickingButtons.java for the ID 4171?
You should have something similar to

case 4171: c.getPA().spellTeleport(X_COORD, Y_COORD, Z_COORD, "modern"); break;

Again, similar.
You will need to modify the x y and z.

Sometimes, or should I say most of the times, the coordinates will be in Config.java, but that’s not always the case.

If it’s different, or a part of editing that is confusing you, then post the code for the case 4171 and I’ll explain what you need to do.
